OL,4,G2355FDynasties
OL,5,     GDocumentary following endangered
OL,6,     Gspecies fighting for their
OL,7,     Gsurvival. David, a chimpanzee in
OL,8,     GSenegal, tries to overcome
OL,9,     Gthreats to his leadership and
OL,10,     Gensure an heir.
OL,11,G0055FDynasties II
OL,12,     GIn the wild Patagonian mountains,
OL,13,     Ga puma battles to raise her
OL,14,     Gbiggest litter yet.
OL,15,G0155FThe Green Planet
OL,16,     GTropical rainforests are plant
OL,17,     Gbattlegrounds. New filming
OL,18,     Gtechniques allow us to enter the
OL,19,     Gworld of plants to see it from
OL,20,     Gtheir perspective and on their
OL,21,     Gtimescale.
